data.description: SELLERS ARE MOTIVATED!!!!!! PRICE REDUCED! This home offers GREAT schools, Peace & Quite & its only 15-20 minutes away from 380, providing a quick access to the city! Well Maintained 1.5 Story Home Situated on 1+ Acre Lot Features 4 Bdrms, 2 Baths, 2 Car Gar + Office. Open Flr Plan Provides Tons of Natural Light Thru-out the Spacious Living Rm & Lg Island Kitchen with Stainless Steel Appl's, Granite Counters & Brkfast Bar. Master Suite Displays a Window Seat, Dual Sinks, Framed Mirrors, HUGE Shower & Custom Closet! Upstairs Flex Space, Make It What You Want, has Recessed Lighting, Wood Beams & Spacious Closet. Utility-Mud Rm with Built-in Cabinets & Space for 2nd Fridge! Area Unincorporated, Livestock Permitted. 1200sf Pad Ready for your Dream Workshop! ATTN VA's; you can possibly get a 3.3% interest rate assumable loan!!!
